              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Lu sample consisted of two disks made of the same",
                "naturally isotopic Lu material. Both disks had a",
                "diameter of 20 mm and a thickness of 1.2 mm. The",
                "masses of the disks are 6.387 g and 6.295 g.",
                "The elemental composition of the two samples are as",
                "follows: natLu - 96.45 w %; Hf - 0.05 w %; Th,",
                "Pm, Gd, Tb, Dy, and Yb are present, but no quantitative",
                "analysis was done."
              ]
